  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ac5fa56a-d18f-4cd0-98cb-598645b3c4d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8a8062b4-82cd-4698-b8a4-3c7360e80e86\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6bc-9523-11ed-b843-bd42b352cb29\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 52</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-0c6b155e-dd75-4c5c-bd4e-7cef7077dc60\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6bd-9523-11ed-b843-1b60ca7058fa\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-96f8f6db-5b67-4e5b-9494-c50670369221\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6be-9523-11ed-b843-d587fe00ad4f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 관리자페이지 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-605384be-1793-4134-96ef-98ecd48270eb\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6bf-9523-11ed-b843-6ffc60d4aa6a\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 관리자페이지 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 관리자페이지의 기획 및 스토리보딩 작업에 집중해 보겠습니다. 이제 2023년 다시 시작입니다. 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-38b44d51-4053-450c-ae69-e32a7ec76b8f\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6c0-9523-11ed-b843-03e14fa07e09\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5977623c-f00f-4644-b0e5-b3be60018242\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6c1-9523-11ed-b843-2d6a72b020c0\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc523518-cfbe-4356-8d2f-036605e0f2bd\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afb6c2-9523-11ed-b843-4d94ad59343f\" style=\"color:#444444;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>관리자페이지의 시작</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line4\" id=\"SE-78d69b88-5850-470e-9280-26f29de20e79\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line4 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bcd54614-343a-40f8-95cc-2def32900f43\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f217c889-c03a-43fb-b62e-f2905d7539d3\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13afddd3-9523-11ed-b843-456e6fa44da1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 관리자 페이지까지 겸한 스토리보딩을 연재하겠습니다. vba를 통한 엑셀프로그램을 11회까지 연재했습니다. 1차로 완성은 했고 2차 개발을 준비중에 있습니다. 이 엑셀에서 관리해야 할 부분을 (주)파파스컴퍼니 관리자페이지에 녹이겠습니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-table se-l-table_layout1\" id=\"SE-e1863edd-d735-439c-9982-444755c6b5c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-table se-l-table_layout1 se-section-align-\" style=\"width: 42%;\">\n<div class=\"se-table-container\">\n<table class=\"se-table-content\" style=\"border-style:solid;border-width:1px 0px 0px 1px;border-color:#00b3f2;\">\n<tbody><tr class=\"se-tr\"><td class=\"se-cell\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"width: 100.0%; height: 255.0px; border-style:solid;border-width:0px 1px 1px 0px;border-color:#00b3f2; background-color: #f7f7f7;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e19c688-fa31-499e-acc2-31a1b9fe5cad\" style=\"line-height:2.3;\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13b004e4-9523-11ed-b843-d19be70e6516\" style=\"\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13b004e5-9523-11ed-b843-c5ec76392aff\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-13b004e6-9523-11ed-b843-897d031c53a9\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> 사이트 관리자페이지 개발진행  v1.0 ::</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummyeongjo se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b004e7-9523-11ed-b843-2fbd0217d8a5\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>:</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4dabbe4-7d58-4f45-8c67-68433a415c41\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13b004e8-9523-11ed-b843-85040f5252ab\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-13b004e9-9523-11ed-b843-31ba9d0d6c9e\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b> 사이트</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f61d0b7-a402-47d7-83c4-28940c3e8bca\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-13b004ea-9523-11ed-b843-9b7dabf5fabc\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>   관리자페이지</b></span></p></div><div class=\"se-module se-module-text\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-65c6c45e-b7af-4bd7-aef6-5e8153375513\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs34 se-ff-nanummyeongjo\" id=\"SE-13b004eb-9523-11ed-b843-8363b769ff00\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>   작업</b></span></p></div>\n</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e73b85ca-5159-4262-b4bc-b734230105b9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-053976cb-9626-495f-99a8-dad329cb2976\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13b02bfc-9523-11ed-b843-e9f904a68eef\" style=\"\">디자인 요소</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b78b156d-0d15-48d1-8ef1-8a165a7d1917\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-1f07239f-f974-4427-ba47-68f691adeae4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d6c73ce7-4daf-426e-8c40-870b0ba7d23d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs38 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02bfd-9523-11ed-b843-b97e6513c111\" style=\"color:#333333;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인 요소 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02bfe-9523-11ed-b843-dd71d1c8e5bd\" style=\"color:#9c9c9c;background-color:#ffffff;\">Design Menu</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-71474e71-34d5-4c57-b483-44dab1cd989c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02bff-9523-11ed-b843-51787740f445\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인 요소는 디자인에 필요한 요소를 정의한 창입니다. 디자인 요소는 이 디자인 템플릿에 어떤 것이 필요하고 어떤 부분이 수정이 가능한지를 관리하는 것입니다. 물론 제약이 존재합니다. 예를 들어 32페이지 카다로그가 한 페이지, 한 페이지를 다 수정할 수 있는 주문요소를 정의하는것은 불가능합니다. 하지만 명함의 경우 이름을 바꾼다거나 로고를 교체한다거나 하는것은 가능합니다. 그 부분을 정의하고 교체관리하는 요소를 만드는 작업입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a54af6dd-f8dc-4942-b85f-9d0ffcc5ec37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0a306c1-ba4c-48f3-a876-5389e3184202\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d07a261d-92c0-474a-8301-cd5e11505a2b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02c00-9523-11ed-b843-2930de251a20\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 명함을 예로 들고 디자인 요소를 정의해 보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e16df94f-aed2-4142-b67c-18123b93cb15\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-732b9c1a-1795-4702-8831-b58e5106ef56\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7d0c725d-1d12-4e16-aadc-adbb52a97758\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53cef09b-b735-4d8c-9fe6-396e41ce7ee6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02c01-9523-11ed-b843-af9ae5221595\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>1. 로고</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02c02-9523-11ed-b843-8f2045a2395a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 로고는 디자인 템플릿에 맞는 사이즈를 주면 좋습니다. 회사 로고를 교체하는 것은 중요한 작업입니다. 로고는 png, pdf, ai등을 주셔야 합니다. 투명이미지나 원본이 아니면 작업이 어렵습니다. 비트맵이나 벡터에 대한 사항은 다음을 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7bfabcd8-5dcf-4492-869f-99ed70413ec6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b02c03-9523-11ed-b843-a5e67d08a553\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cb67e6d-5675-43b4-af74-49b94b133358\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90decb80-0357-438d-be46-3f6a4150395e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b05314-9523-11ed-b843-b39884042ed1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>2. 슬로건</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b05315-9523-11ed-b843-e7388830496f\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 슬로건은 회사의 메인테마를 결정하는 키워드입니다. 없으면 허전함을 감소하고 업로드를 하지 않는 것입니다. 대부분 슬로건을 삽입하지 않는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0c78348-e89a-4d2d-bc15-7de86108247a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a26-9523-11ed-b843-8f98ecb004de\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-81478f3f-7a93-4a77-802a-63dca2bbaaca\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a27-9523-11ed-b843-cfef1a0517a8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>3. 제 2의 로고</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a28-9523-11ed-b843-af346de33c0c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 제2의 로고가 없다면 4번을 2번 자리에 삽입하고 3, 4번 부분은 없는 명함이 될 수 있습니다. 만약에 3, 4번이 없고 4번 내용을 2번에 삽입한다면 아래와 같은 명함으로 디자인 될것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1022e66a-8d47-426e-9571-956c81636c07\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-88a7befb-8162-4dea-8fa2-986280b606bf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8df422fc-004b-4f9c-a531-32d23c390143\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a29-9523-11ed-b843-0ffc042aeaa6\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>4. 분야</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2a-9523-11ed-b843-0f05cca3775d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 사업분야를 적는 칸입니다. 줄이나 폭제한은 있을 수 있지만 맞춰서 작업이 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f0b16604-c37f-4665-9dda-b42a9e32b803\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2b-9523-11ed-b843-e9c9cc65b895\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa2488fe-5635-4ee0-9507-a2bc3efdc069\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2c-9523-11ed-b843-9b188c0c83b8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>5. 회사명</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2d-9523-11ed-b843-c153a1c39f9a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 회사명입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8fb507b-caea-4575-a1aa-032ae24c62d1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2e-9523-11ed-b843-055456e8898e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3e62deae-a585-4b5d-a6a5-93f45807d7d2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a2f-9523-11ed-b843-d18ac5719dbe\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>6. 직책</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a30-9523-11ed-b843-9dc0aa3a0e58\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 직책입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-20caa3c8-b54f-4336-93a9-838baf48f834\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a31-9523-11ed-b843-510964a9f36d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b1470431-6775-42e0-b1f7-0036a47d0794\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b07a32-9523-11ed-b843-49af5a1d5496\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>7. 이름</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a143-9523-11ed-b843-6b847f1eae02\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 이름입니다. 영문까지 포함한다면 디자인을 변경할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fd220c2f-4097-41a2-b970-05d5bafceb49\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a144-9523-11ed-b843-f5b1da8edb69\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c3be4bb-9bc8-4519-b123-65a1f121a144\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a145-9523-11ed-b843-a9e94a9558c9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>8. 핸드폰번호</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a146-9523-11ed-b843-4db9c8dd8c6d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 핸드폰 번호입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0bc3e50-6d64-41e7-8a5f-f4e4425fd9be\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a147-9523-11ed-b843-39ab270837a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-08b4d06c-2145-480b-bda0-1e8f7d37fc6e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a148-9523-11ed-b843-b3ec0af8bcf3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>9. 회사번호</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a149-9523-11ed-b843-f3e89ecf1628\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 회사 전화번호입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6f753529-2b63-4a5d-9deb-839fcbaa1f4e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14a-9523-11ed-b843-37d4a3f60e79\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3db79fde-9a97-4f8c-8664-4ee75c7c43e3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14b-9523-11ed-b843-bf2a9b5497fc\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>10. 이메일</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14c-9523-11ed-b843-5f70eada9bad\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 개인이나 회사 이메일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ed254f3-f288-4bae-81e1-5036a6123881\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14d-9523-11ed-b843-ffe1a3d854be\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00b982ff-66b6-4724-b14e-97e11aa984e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14e-9523-11ed-b843-1b23e4529e37\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>11. 주소</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a14f-9523-11ed-b843-2daae38df564\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : 회사 주소입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f5062b65-e09b-4ada-9648-2fb94f271830\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0a150-9523-11ed-b843-9dfe72f6ab98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1af392de-4586-451f-b02e-daad0f557409\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c861-9523-11ed-b843-9319848ab4da\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ff9300;\"><b>12. sns</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c862-9523-11ed-b843-8bb1deefd0ba\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"> : sns관련 정보입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-37ac1ce4-ca9b-47b5-8cdd-32ac5b679dd7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0798b61f-9342-46f6-b25e-e1427120fff1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3767c1bf-5ebe-4bb8-8204-db74a6b2311f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-51b5c529-750d-402b-8cc9-d8480e572e62\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c863-9523-11ed-b843-f98f9aecc7a9\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">지금은 초보 수준의 기획단계입니다. 디테일한 UI는 변경될 수 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b3ef3abb-2524-4772-9107-0e9fc527d58e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c864-9523-11ed-b843-8779cc358224\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">1번 부터 12번까지 넣을 수 있는 정보를 관리하는 페이지입니다. 요소의 종류는 더 고민중입니다. 텍스트를 한글과 영문 또는 숫자로 구분할 지도 고민중이고 파일도 비트맵이미지와 벡터를 나눌지도 고민중입니다. 파일에는 파일 종류를 두고 제한을 둘것인지 또는 동영상파일은 어떻게 받을 것인지를 고민중에 있습니다. 2차 기획 완료편에서 모두 정리하도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d948712-84e8-454f-a4d5-553dd7d20a82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222981431642/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fecfde3e-c90b-4eaa-aeab-563295ff2ff1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13b0c865-9523-11ed-b843-f73b8e757400\" style=\"\">홈페이지UI</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dde88aa3-e53e-4179-ba56-bb0352430a10\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a97ba4b2-4226-4495-afab-953e8e09d063\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c866-9523-11ed-b843-e5fec7df4c66\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d221785f-270c-4319-918e-b6eff75d97ce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-13b0c867-9523-11ed-b843-4ff3e65cf659\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">프론트에서는 다음과 같이 표현되어 정보를 받을 수 있도록 구성될 예정입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42d8ce45-ca03-474d-b2d1-bb322032e00c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-00ff6254-3d78-4420-9fde-74baa3c00a1e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}